"    Chronic pulmonary embolism",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 354px; height: 308px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Pulmonary angiogram shows mosaic oligemia with localization of pulmonary blood flow to the lower lobes. This may be regarded as a Westermark's sign with oligemia affecting the subtended pulmonary parenchyma of the upper lobes.",
