"     George L Bakris, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?6/60/7113/contributors\">",
"     Bernard J Gersh, MB, ChB, DPhil, FRCP, MACC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
