"     <br>",
"      Additional data from:&nbsp;Olsen EA, Whittaker S, Kim YH, et al. Clinical end points and response criteria in mycosis fungoides and S&eacute;zary syndrome: a consensus statement of the International Society for Cutaneous Lymphomas, the United States Cutaneous Lymphoma Consortium, and the Cutaneous Lymphoma Task Force of the European Organisation for Research and Treatment of Cancer. J Clin Oncol 2011; 29:2598.",
"     </br>",
